"any size, from small documents to large PDF files."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:133
msgid "Conversion Questions"
msgstr "Conversion Questions"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:138
msgid "How do I convert PDF to Word without losing formatting?"
msgstr "How do I convert PDF to Word without losing formatting?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:142
msgid ""
"To convert PDF to Word without losing formatting, use Convertica's PDF to "
"Word converter. Simply upload your PDF file, and our advanced conversion "
"engine preserves text formatting, images, tables, and layout. The conversion"
" maintains fonts, colors, spacing, and structure of your original document. "
"All conversions are free and require no registration."
msgstr ""
"To convert PDF to Word without losing formatting, use Convertica's PDF to "
"Word converter. Simply upload your PDF file, and our advanced conversion "
"engine preserves text formatting, images, tables, and layout. The conversion"
" maintains fonts, colors, spacing, and structure of your original document. "
"All conversions are free and require no registration."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:148 templates/frontend/index.html:38
#: utils_site/src/frontend/views.py:1212
msgid "How do I convert PDF to Word?"
msgstr "How do I convert PDF to Word?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:152 utils_site/src/frontend/views.py:1214
msgid ""
"To convert PDF to Word, simply upload your PDF file using the upload button "
"or drag and drop it into the upload zone. Click the convert button and wait "
"for the conversion to complete. Download your converted Word document using "
"the download button. The conversion is free and requires no registration."
msgstr ""
"To convert PDF to Word, simply upload your PDF file using the upload button "
"or drag and drop it into the upload zone. Click the convert button and wait "
"for the conversion to complete. Download your converted Word document using "
"the download button. The conversion is free and requires no registration."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:158
msgid "How do I convert Word to PDF?"
msgstr "How do I convert Word to PDF?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:162
msgid ""
"Upload your Word document (.doc or .docx), click convert, and download your "
"PDF. The conversion preserves formatting and layout of your original "
"document."
msgstr ""
"Upload your Word document (.doc or .docx), click convert, and download your "
"PDF. The conversion preserves formatting and layout of your original "
"document."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:168
msgid "Can I convert PDF to JPG?"
msgstr "Can I convert PDF to JPG?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:172
msgid ""
"Yes, you can convert PDF pages to JPG images. Select the page you want to "
"convert or convert all pages. You can also choose the image quality (DPI) "
"from 72 to 600."
msgstr ""
"Yes, you can convert PDF pages to JPG images. Select the page you want to "
"convert or convert all pages. You can also choose the image quality (DPI) "
"from 72 to 600."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:178
msgid "How do I convert images to PDF?"
msgstr "How do I convert images to PDF?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:182
msgid ""
"Upload one or multiple JPG/JPEG images, arrange them in the desired order, "
"and click convert. All images will be combined into a single PDF document "
"with automatic A4 formatting."
msgstr ""
"Upload one or multiple JPG/JPEG images, arrange them in the desired order, "
"and click convert. All images will be combined into a single PDF document "
"with automatic A4 formatting."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:188
msgid "Can I extract tables from PDF to Excel?"
msgstr "Can I extract tables from PDF to Excel?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:192
msgid ""
"Yes, you can extract tables from PDF files and convert them to Excel format."
" Upload your PDF, and Convertica will extract all tables and save them in an"
" Excel file."
msgstr ""
"Yes, you can extract tables from PDF files and convert them to Excel format."
" Upload your PDF, and Convertica will extract all tables and save them in an"
" Excel file."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:201
msgid "Editing & Organization"
msgstr "Editing & Organization"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:206
msgid "How do I merge PDF online free without watermark?"
msgstr "How do I merge PDF online free without watermark?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:210
msgid ""
"To merge PDF online free without watermark, use Convertica's PDF merger. Go "
"to the Merge PDF page, select multiple PDF files, arrange them in the "
"desired order using drag and drop, and click merge. All selected files will "
"be combined into a single PDF document with no watermark added. The merged "
"PDF maintains the quality of original files."
msgstr ""
"To merge PDF online free without watermark, use Convertica's PDF merger. Go "
"to the Merge PDF page, select multiple PDF files, arrange them in the "
"desired order using drag and drop, and click merge. All selected files will "
"be combined into a single PDF document with no watermark added. The merged "
"PDF maintains the quality of original files."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:216 utils_site/src/frontend/views.py:1234
msgid "How do I merge multiple PDF files?"
msgstr "How do I merge multiple PDF files?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:220
msgid ""
"To merge PDF files, go to the Merge PDF page, select multiple PDF files, "
"arrange them in the desired order using drag and drop, and click merge. All "
"selected files will be combined into a single PDF document."
msgstr ""
"To merge PDF files, go to the Merge PDF page, select multiple PDF files, "
"arrange them in the desired order using drag and drop, and click merge. All "
"selected files will be combined into a single PDF document."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:226
msgid "Can I split a PDF into separate files?"
msgstr "Can I split a PDF into separate files?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:230
msgid ""
"Yes, you can split a PDF into separate files. Upload your PDF, choose how to"
" split it (by page range or every N pages), and download the resulting "
"files."
msgstr ""
"Yes, you can split a PDF into separate files. Upload your PDF, choose how to"
" split it (by page range or every N pages), and download the resulting "
"files."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:236
msgid "How do I compress PDF to under 1MB for email?"
msgstr "How do I compress PDF to under 1MB for email?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:240
msgid ""
"To compress PDF to under 1MB for email, use Convertica's PDF compressor. "
"Upload your PDF file, select the high compression level, and click compress."
" The tool will reduce the file size while maintaining acceptable quality for"
" email attachments. You can preview the compressed file size before "
"downloading."
msgstr ""
"To compress PDF to under 1MB for email, use Convertica's PDF compressor. "
"Upload your PDF file, select the high compression level, and click compress."
" The tool will reduce the file size while maintaining acceptable quality for"
" email attachments. You can preview the compressed file size before "
"downloading."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:246
msgid "How do I compress a PDF file?"
msgstr "How do I compress a PDF file?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:250
msgid ""
"Upload your PDF file, select the compression level (low, medium, or high), "
"and click compress. The file size will be reduced while maintaining "
"acceptable quality."
msgstr ""
"Upload your PDF file, select the compression level (low, medium, or high), "
"and click compress. The file size will be reduced while maintaining "
"acceptable quality."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:256
msgid "Can I rotate PDF pages?"
msgstr "Can I rotate PDF pages?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:260
msgid ""
"Yes, you can rotate PDF pages by 90, 180, or 270 degrees. Select the pages "
"you want to rotate and choose the rotation angle."
msgstr ""
"Yes, you can rotate PDF pages by 90, 180, or 270 degrees. Select the pages "
"you want to rotate and choose the rotation angle."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:266
msgid "How do I add a watermark to PDF?"
msgstr "How do I add a watermark to PDF?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:270
msgid ""
"Upload your PDF, choose between text or image watermark, set the position "
"and transparency, and apply. The watermark will be added to all pages or "
"selected pages."
msgstr ""
"Upload your PDF, choose between text or image watermark, set the position "
"and transparency, and apply. The watermark will be added to all pages or "
"selected pages."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:279
msgid "Security & Privacy"
msgstr "Security & Privacy"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:284 templates/frontend/index.html:54
#: utils_site/src/frontend/views.py:1241
msgid "Is my data secure?"
msgstr "Is my data secure?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:288 utils_site/src/frontend/views.py:1243
msgid ""
"Yes, your data is secure. All files are processed securely and automatically"
" deleted immediately after conversion. We do not store your files, and your "
"privacy is our top priority. You can also protect your PDFs with password "
"encryption."
msgstr ""
"Yes, your data is secure. All files are processed securely and automatically"
" deleted immediately after conversion. We do not store your files, and your "
"privacy is our top priority. You can also protect your PDFs with password "
"encryption."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:294
#: utils_site/src/frontend/tool_configs/pdf_security.py:91
msgid "How do I protect a PDF with a password?"
msgstr "How do I protect a PDF with a password?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:298
msgid ""
"Upload your PDF, enter a password (and optionally an owner password), and "
"click protect. The PDF will be encrypted and require a password to open."
msgstr ""
"Upload your PDF, enter a password (and optionally an owner password), and "
"click protect. The PDF will be encrypted and require a password to open."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:304
msgid "Can I remove password protection from a PDF?"
msgstr "Can I remove password protection from a PDF?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:308
msgid ""
"Yes, if you know the password, you can unlock a protected PDF. Upload the "
"protected PDF, enter the password, and click unlock. The password protection"
" will be removed."
msgstr ""
"Yes, if you know the password, you can unlock a protected PDF. Upload the "
"protected PDF, enter the password, and click unlock. The password protection"
" will be removed."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:314
msgid "Are my files stored on your servers?"
msgstr "Are my files stored on your servers?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:318
msgid ""
"No, your files are not stored on our servers. Files are processed "
"immediately and automatically deleted after conversion. We do not keep "
"copies of your documents."
msgstr ""
"No, your files are not stored on our servers. Files are processed "
"immediately and automatically deleted after conversion. We do not keep "
"copies of your documents."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:327
msgid "Technical Questions"
msgstr "Technical Questions"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:332
msgid "What browsers are supported?"
msgstr "What browsers are supported?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:336
msgid ""
"Convertica works on all modern browsers including Chrome, Firefox, Safari, "
"Edge, and Opera. The website is also mobile-friendly and works on "
"smartphones and tablets."
msgstr ""
"Convertica works on all modern browsers including Chrome, Firefox, Safari, "
"Edge, and Opera. The website is also mobile-friendly and works on "
"smartphones and tablets."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:342
msgid "How long does conversion take?"
msgstr "How long does conversion take?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:346
msgid ""
"Conversion time depends on file size and complexity. Most conversions "
"complete in seconds. Larger files may take a minute or two. The progress is "
"shown during conversion."
msgstr ""
"Conversion time depends on file size and complexity. Most conversions "
"complete in seconds. Larger files may take a minute or two. The progress is "
"shown during conversion."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:352
msgid "What if conversion fails?"
msgstr "What if conversion fails?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:356
msgid ""
"If conversion fails, please check that your file is not corrupted and is in "
"a supported format. Try again, and if the problem persists, contact our "
"support team."
msgstr ""
"If conversion fails, please check that your file is not corrupted and is in "
"a supported format. Try again, and if the problem persists, contact our "
"support team."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:362
msgid "Can I use Convertica on mobile devices?"
msgstr "Can I use Convertica on mobile devices?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:366
msgid ""
"Yes, Convertica is fully responsive and works on mobile devices. You can "
"convert, edit, and organize PDFs directly from your smartphone or tablet."
msgstr ""
"Yes, Convertica is fully responsive and works on mobile devices. You can "
"convert, edit, and organize PDFs directly from your smartphone or tablet."

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:377
msgid "Still have questions?"
msgstr "Still have questions?"

#: templates/frontend/faq.html:380
msgid ""
"If you couldn't find the answer you're looking for, feel free to contact us."
msgstr ""
"If you couldn't find the answer you're looking for, feel free to contact us."

